s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n重慶魔法 - 咖喱<br />\n真係好似...咖喱黎嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4ef55c45a237b1844de32055c677785ba07306","tid":1666341,"uid":34367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:17:40.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲組團去食"},{"pid":"4f06cdeef98785fdbe10a9aeddb1dd8d6efa8a3d","tid":1666341,"uid":80151,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:28:43.000Z","msg":"入門口好多人好熱情喇 成日叫你食下佢果間野<br />\n即使我試唔到7E咖喱王<br />\n落lift 行返轉地下<br />\n途中好多人問你食唔食喇<br />\n<br />\n突然有個男仔行埋黎： 好好食嫁 試下喇<br />\n因為佢有禮貌 所以跟左佢行上左一層<br />\n入左某間野喇<br />\n地下上一層既<br />\n名唔開喇<br />\n<br />\n有個2人set $220再+10%<br />\n咖喱角2個<br />\n香烤雞2件<br />\n咖喱蕃茄雞<br />\n菠菜芝士<br />\n薄飯<br />\n野飲2杯（揀左奶昔）<br />\n<br />\n因為up圖太慢既關係<br />\nup左呢張食曬既圖先<br />\n今晚返屋企再up相<br />\n下個回應寫食評<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KEGY5xv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKEGY5xv.png&h=6e965f1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"afdfb21148d4e34809711f84bd69150c5ecfb4bf","tid":1666341,"uid":158411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65823d8b1439705c6d06cbf4ad7383c60115f31f","tid":1666341,"uid":222499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:11:23.000Z","msg":"其實有無套餐, openrice只係見到佢散叫menu"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:32:39.000Z","msg":"有冇一人套餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"841032866ce8b4f52c52278b3059e8c5bd9626ab","tid":1666341,"uid":262032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:33:59.000Z","msg":"手足好波 遲d去食下先"},{"pid":"005e0e20c974fbef40e0a4b9856094afe2b9e8a0","tid":1666341,"uid":80151,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"4f06cdeef98785fdbe10a9aeddb1dd8d6efa8a3d","tid":1666341,"uid":80151,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:28:43.000Z","msg":"入門口好多人好熱情喇 成日叫你食下佢果間野<br />\n即使我試唔到7E咖喱王<br />\n落lift 行返轉地下<br />\n途中好多人問你食唔食喇<br />\n<br />\n突然有個男仔行埋黎： 好好食嫁 試下喇<br />\n因為佢有禮貌 所以跟左佢行上左一層<br />\n入左某間野喇<br />\n地下上一層既<br />\n名唔開喇<br />\n<br />\n有個2人set $220再+10%<br />\n咖喱角2個<br />\n香烤雞2件<br />\n咖喱蕃茄雞<br />\n菠菜芝士<br />\n薄飯<br />\n野飲2杯（揀左奶昔）<br />\n<br />\n因為up圖太慢既關係<br />\nup左呢張食曬既圖先<br />\n今晚返屋企再up相<br />\n下個回應寫食評<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KEGY5xv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKEGY5xv.png&h=6e965f1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:49:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z9BKgLZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz9BKgLZ.jpg&h=0b408d11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咖喱角2個<br />\n都係雜菜 四角形 大大個<br />\n烤得好脆<br />\n中間以咖喱薯仔為主<br />\n配上薄荷醬<br />\n香脆可口<br />\n<br />\n香烤雞2件<br />\n印度野多數整定再翻熱<br />\n烤雞唔例外 燶得濟<br />\n無咩味<br />\n重申 佢係烤雞 無味好正常<br />\n<br />\n咖喱蕃茄雞<br />\n咖喱好好食<br />\n有濃濃茄味<br />\n雞件無骨<br />\n本餐最出色！<br />\n落足香料 小小辣 三小辣都可能無<br />\n<br />\n菠菜芝士<br />\n太肥 菠菜攪到變汁<br />\n芝士成舊上 太肥<br />\n所以食左2啖就放棄<br />\n<br />\n薄飯<br />\n即叫即整<br />\n香脆 熱<br />\n正常<br />\n<br />\n野飲2杯（揀左奶昔）<br />\n奶昔係薯通乳酪味 <br />\n<br />\n$242 完<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRUG3ra.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRUG3ra.png&h=a84d519f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"321328f7fac1e697b442ae1e25f480990d4aa5a2","tid":1666341,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:57:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ffad57fe6ad912a1b363052ec788e1bd0dad38","tid":1666341,"uid":38461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35837d497d4b9b2a2ce65dc7ed5b3932204112b5","tid":1666341,"uid":80151,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:13:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dzkGiM3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdzkGiM3.png&h=9227fd48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n重慶魔法 - 咖喱<br />\n真係好似...咖喱黎嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smil